{"tid":553782,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[置頂]今日polySU選舉lastday,票投1號防紅底2號","createTime":"2018-02-07T23:10:35.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-08T00:33:06.000Z","uid":47359,"like":5,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"8251e6d42ecac66d4b8a22d1f59af702de89b34a","tid":553782,"uid":47359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-07T23:10:35.000Z","msg":"理大學生會2號莊偽本土 真赤化<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/t/550803/1?ref=android\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/t/550803/1?ref=android</a><br />\n<br />\nLIHKG @ Android"},{"pid":"919cab87c17f4f0222563b76dc2a6e3983fca0eb","tid":553782,"uid":47359,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8251e6d42ecac66d4b8a22d1f59af702de89b34a","tid":553782,"uid":47359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-07T23:10:35.000Z","msg":"理大學生會2號莊偽本土 真赤化<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/t/550803/1?ref=android\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/t/550803/1?ref=android</a><br />\n<br />\nLIHKG @ Android"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-07T23:12:30.000Z","msg":"借隔籬post用下<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<blockquote>事源係論壇 聽到兩支莊比人問政治聯繫<br />\n除左理凝有民主黨intern evp<br />\n煥賢既財政 施子健 竟然幫過民建聯李慧琼助選<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/05/134322_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F05%2F134322_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=99812a35&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n我心諗 唔係掛 咁都搵佢做大莊財政？<br />\n愈諗愈唔對路 於是搵下資料<br />\n比我搵到佢去中聯辦實習團啲資料<br />\n個團係2017暑假 新鮮滖熱辣 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/05/134358_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F05%2F134358_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=6ee90332&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/05/134402_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F05%2F134402_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=0e89e308&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n個財政上年都選過大莊<br />\n最後支莊「被流選」<br />\n因為啲莊員比人鼓勵quit<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/05/134412_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F05%2F134412_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=afb067e6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n之後個財政再去中共交流團<br />\n今年再去選多次大莊？ 仲要扮本土咁岩？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/05/134424_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F05%2F134424_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=8a698590&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n佢個P洪子健仲話佢係比屋企人迫去助選<br />\n迫？ 佢笑得咁開心<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/05/134429_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F05%2F134429_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=59bac73b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n仲有好多感想<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/05/134436_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F05%2F134436_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=200e267d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/05/134439_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F05%2F134439_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=f88343d5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n上得共青團微博 唔係中共屬意+自己人邊會上到？<br />\n根本純正紅色血統<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/05/134450_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F05%2F134450_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=4d9b599e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n後尾再發現原來個財政張提名表格衰左<br />\n之後佢支莊話如果贏左一定會補選佢<br />\n嘩 避風頭唔使出ocon 之後再係評議會過會上 陰陰濕濕<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/05/134501_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F05%2F134501_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=aad3a251&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/05/134504_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F05%2F134504_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=54787cf6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n(上年4號莊煥理)<br />\n再發現原來煥賢個p + ivp<br />\n上年同個財政係同一支大莊<br />\n邊有可能個莊員去完中共交流團都唔知？<br />\n都唔知係有份共謀 定 天真無政治智慧<br />\n如果有份共謀 就成支莊誠信破產<br />\n如果天真無政治智慧 佢支莊都唔知仲有邊個係鬼<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/05/134518_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F05%2F134518_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=ce852a12&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n諗諗下其實個P洪子鍵都好有問題<br />\n上年4號莊話緊學校校董會高層個陣<br />\n煥賢個P (上年4號個個EVP) 竟然退選？<br />\n你唔夠膽定助攻呀？<br />\n<br />\n再講煥賢個IVP做評議會秘書個陣<br />\n唔跟程序亂收form 遲得好離譜都照收 <br />\n(可以問返評議會啲人)<br />\n為左討好啲soc 規則都唔跟 <br />\n再聽聞佢地想拎內地學生協會啲票 真心咩？<br />\n<br />\n公義？ 程序？你地同對家有咩分別？<br />\n點知你地係咪扮本土玩膠出賣poly人？<br />\n點知你地係咪鬼 之後穿su櫃桶？ <br />\n畢竟依加su好似有幾百萬儲備 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/05/134532_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F05%2F134532_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=71a19e80&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/05/134536_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F05%2F134536_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=671dd086&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n比個機會人啦！<br />\n too simple, sometimes naive<br />\n仲有資格上大莊？<br />\n一直比你地蒙在鼓裏<br />\n<br />\n#唔好學鄭若驊話自己政治敏感度不足<br />\n#信錯你地班人 <br />\n#真理愈辯愈明 <br />\n#allin2 #allin共匪 #allin弱智<br />\n<br />\n利申: 做過su打雜</blockquote>"},{"pid":"d6c07b2d29a84e72f42ae3bc2a141f189105f059","tid":553782,"uid":116530,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-07T23:12:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/08/071253_2f8b3b8a0047505843a29513521b3595.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F08%2F071253_2f8b3b8a0047505843a29513521b3595.png&h=e8f9444f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2ea6c7e952b118dc4c169f6bcb126693f08a60f6","tid":553782,"uid":47359,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"d6c07b2d29a84e72f42ae3bc2a141f189105f059","tid":553782,"uid":116530,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-07T23:12:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/08/071253_2f8b3b8a0047505843a29513521b3595.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F08%2F071253_2f8b3b8a0047505843a29513521b3595.png&h=e8f9444f&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-07T23:14:12.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">返你老母工咩五毛生田繪梨花<br />\n你喺poly返工呀？<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span>"},{"pid":"f6a505600c1e25ce346482ed2ca79ce8d5a3fde9","tid":553782,"uid":47359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"